1. Purchase an Item
Click on item link
Click "Add to cart" button
Click "Proceed to checkout" button
Click "Proceed to checkout" button
Enter valid email address
Enter valid password
Click Sign In Button
Click "Proceed to checkout" button
Click "terms of service" checkbox
Click "Pay by bank wire" button
Click "I confirm my order" button

2. Send message through Contact Us
Click on Contact Us link
Select a heading from Subject Heading dropdown
Enter an email address
Upload picture
Type in a message
Click Send Button

3. Send a reset password email
Navigate to URL
Click on Sign In Button
Click "Forgot your password?" link
Input email address
Click "Retrieve Password" button

4.Sign into account and view order
Click on Sign In Button
Enter valid email
Enter valid password
Click Sign In Button
Click Order History and Details
Click on PDF button

5. Sign into account with valid email and password
Click on Sign In Button
Enter valid email
Enter valid password
Click Sign In Button

6. Search for item and purchase
Enter search term into searchbar
Click search button
Select item to purchase
Click "Add to cart" button
Click "Proceed to checkout" button
Click "Proceed to checkout" button
Enter valid email address
Enter valid password
Click Sign In Button
Click "Proceed to checkout" button
Click "terms of service" checkbox
Click "Pay by bank wire" button
Click "I confirm my order" button

7.Remove item from shopping cart
Click on item link
Add item to cart
Close modal window
Click on shopping cart button
Click on delete button


8. Sign in with valid email and invalid password
Click on sign in button
Enter valid email
Enter invalid password

9. Write a review
Click sign in button
Enter valid email
Enter valid password
Click Sign In button
Click on item link
Click on Write a review button
Select quality rating
Enter title
Enter comment
Click send button


10. Subscribe to newsletter
Enter email in newsletter field
Click submit button

